description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Cutouts!  A game made entirely from felt! Run, duck, jump, and throw objects at your enemies!  Collect buttons for extra lives!  Nine levels across three worlds!  A true indie project, all art, music, and programming made by me!    ****"A delectable work of genius...You'd be hard pressed to find anything more charming at the moment" -DIY
